  "authors": [],
  "body": {
    "comment": "The proposal “Eternl: Path to Sustainability (2026-2027)” (9a020ea7a6a0d813ff08c92bd8300b26077ae69a4b827c4d432ac665120325d7#0) has already been deemed unconstitutional by 4/7 CC members and has subsequently been resubmitted by the proposers (fbb8d1a4a8d6b62f8cd706944a0582b884c2b90187b8fada7953d5c6a33eb5a7#0). Therefore, I vote NO in this instance. I will review the v2 submission and submit my vote with more detailed rationale there."
  },
  "hashAlgorithm": "blake2b-256"
}
